snippet.title: High Court Is Shown Video Of Johnny Depp Smashing Up Kitchen & Throwing Wine Bottle In Drunken Rage
snippet.description:
High Court is shown video of Johnny Depp 'smashing up kitchen and throwing wine bottle in drunken rage at Amber Heard' while he tells her 'You wanna see crazy? I'll give you f***ing crazy' as he denies ever hitting her at blockbuster libel trial

Shocking moment Johnny Depp 'smashes up kitchen and throws wine bottle to the floor in drunken rage. The video filmed by Amber Heard showed Depp smashing up the kitchen he shared with her.
Shocking moment Johnny Depp 'smashes up kitchen and throws bottle'
